snippet.title: FATE: Reawakened Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Mark your calendars and get ready to enter the Dungeon Gate once again! 

FATE: Reawakened will be launching on PC & Console platforms on March 12! Prepare to experience all 4 classic games like you’ve never seen before.
